    Maheshwari Superstar 2025 is a vibrant cultural talent hunt organized by Kendriya Yuva Samiti in collaboration with All Kshetriya Yuva Samitis.
Scheduled for 28th & 29th June 2025 at Maheshwari Bhavan, Andheri (West), the event offers a platform for Maheshwari youth to showcase their talents in dance, music, comedy, poetry, and more. 
With categories like Dancing Superstar, Musical Instrument Superstar, Mr. & Ms. Maheshwari, and more, it promises excitement, creativity, and community celebration.
Registration closes on 15th June 2025 – don’t miss your chance to shine!.

    We’re thrilled to announce the first-ever edition of SOBO Shark Tank – South Mumbai Yuva Samiti, happening on 10th September 2025 8:30 PM.

Yes, you read that right—it’s Shark Tank, but this time YOU are the Shark. 🦈

This unique event will give you an immersive experience of the start-up world and ecosystem. You’ll get a chance to:

- Step into the shoes of an investor
- Learn how start-ups think, pitch & scale
- Interact with budding entrepreneurs showcasing their ideas
- Explore how Sharks & Start-ups can grow together
- Network within our Maheshwari community and connect with like-minded people

We’re creating an exciting platform where learning meets opportunity, and we’d love for you to be part of it.

👉 Seats are limited. Register on the MPM App at the earliest to confirm your spot.

Waiting to see you on Wednesday, the 10th of September at 8:30 PM on 1st Floor of Girgaum Maheshwari Bhavan for this game-changing experience.

Please note: This is a paid event, registration is mandatory & seats will be allotted on a first-come, first-served basis.
